[INSTALL NOTES:]

0. Disable your network

2. Close it if it's running (Kill the activtae process in task manager)
3. Open keygen to get your serial 
4. Right click on Activation.reg file & select 'Edit'
5. Now change 'Put Your Serial Here' to your serial
6. Press 'Save'
7. Double click on reg file
7.1 Use firewall to block the program from accessing to the web! (IMPORTANT!)
Note: If you don't use firewall, it will turn back to trial mode after your re-launch it!

8. You can run DLL Fixer & use it online. On Windows 7, serial didn't blocked but on Windows 8.1 it just fly immediately. 
Don't worry, you can use another serial to activate, just follow step 5,6,7 with NET OFF
